      "id": "14339211-5426-4193-a0a4-46b18678241b",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "#Setting up constants\ng = 9.81 #acceleration in ms^-2 due to gravity\nrho = 1.225 #air density in kgm^-3\nmu = 0.47 #drag coefficient\n\n",
